flowRoot.flowPara: For more details visit our github repository:
https://github.com/eYSIP-2017/ eYSIP-2017_Development_of_Web_Interface_for_GH_Farm_Produce
1. Automation of Menial task of produce
logging.
2. Logging details about farm produce
such as weight, image, type, etc.
onto a web based portal.
3. Web interface for Monitoring and
generating analytics about the data.
4. Distribution of farm produce via an
online Portal.
1. An automated system for Farm produce
Monitoring and Logging.
2. A System to generate and plot
analytics about the logged data for
producers.
3. An organised, scalable and secure web
based interface to distribute the Farm
produce.
4. An easy to use and feature rich control
over the entire system for admins.

text.tspan: Development of Web Interface for GH Farm Produce
Hemang Gandhi, Keivan Shah. Mentors: Yogita Mali, Uma Sharma, Parin Chheda.
